high_descs: Turn and move to the end of the wood table, so the green door is on your left.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Turn around and carry the fork to the kitchen sink.
Place the fork in the right side of the sink, turn on the water, and then remove once it is washed.
Turn around and carry the fork to the microwave cart.
Place the fork on top of the tomato closest to you on the cart.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed fork on a tomato on the microwave cart.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the end of the counter.
Pick up the fork from the counter.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Rinse the fork in the sink.
Turn around and approach the microwave.
Put the fork on the table in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed fork on the table in front of the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the door on the right of the room, then turn right towards the table.
Pick up the fork from the table.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Wash the fork in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Place the fork on the microwave stand by the other fork.
anns.task_desc: Wash the fork on the table in the sink and place it next to the other fork by the microwave.
